<h1 class ="hugeTitle">
  Get Growing
</h1>

<div class ="aboutUs">
  <div class="row">	
    <p>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <div class="boxes">
          <%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => session_path(resource_name), :html => {:class => 'form-horizontal'}) do |f| %>
            <%= devise_error_messages! %>
            <fieldset>
              <p><div class="miniAboutTitle">Already a Member?</div></p>
 

              <div class='form-group'>
                <%= f.label :email, :class => 'col-lg-5 control-label' %>
                <div class='col-lg-7'>
                  <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, required: true %>
                </div>
              </div>	
              <div class='form-group'>
                <%= f.label :password, :class => 'col-lg-5 control-label' %>
                <div class='col-lg-7'>
                  <%= f.password_field :password, required: true %>
  		
                  <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
                </div>
              </div>

              <% if devise_mapping.rememberable? -%>
                <div class='form-group'>
                  <%= f.label :remember_me, :class => 'col-lg-5 control-label' %>
                  <div class='col-lg-7'>
                    <%= f.check_box :remember_me %>
                  </div>
                </div>
              <%end%>
              <div class='form-group'>
                <div class='col-lg-12'>
                  <%= f.submit "Log in", :class => 'btn-block' %>
                </div>
              </div>
		
            </fieldset>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </p>
      <p>By signing in you agree to our <%= link_to "Terms & Conditions", page_path("terms") %>.</p>
      <p>We promise we will never sell, rent or share any of your data to/with a third party.</p>
	  <p>We use cookies throughout our website. More information as to how we use cookies, as well as how we handle your personal data, can be found on our <%= link_to "Privacy & Cookies", page_path("privacy_and_cookies") %> page.</p>

    </div>

    <div class="col-md-7">
      <div class="boxes">
        <p><div class="miniAboutTitle">Not joined yet? Let's get growing!</div></p>
        <fieldset>
          <p>Welcome to SeedPod. We'd love to have you on board. When you subscribe, our unique growing programme will provide:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Two varieties of seasonally appropriate vegetable seeds each month</li> 
            <li>Access to our monthly step-by-step guidance</li> 
            <li>'Get Ready' advice to preparea for your first pod</li> 
          </ul>
          <p>Subscribe today for just Â£6.00 per month (inc. VAT), with free delivery, and no contractual tie-in.</p>
		  <p>You will receive your seeds, and gain access to "This Month" guidance, within ten days of subscribing. Until that date you will have access to our "Get Ready" page to help prepare for your first delivery.</p>
	


          <div class='form-group'>
            <div class='col-lg-12'>
              <%= link_to "Subscribe", new_user_registration_path, :class => 'btn btn-block' %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Need more info? Check out our <%= link_to "Any Questions", page_path("faq") %> page, or take a look at our <%= link_to "Sneak Peek", page_path("preview") %> growing guidance page.</p>
  
        </fieldset>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>